Dotfiles
==========
This repository contains config files for my different systems. Each system has
its own branch, and shared changes are made in the main branch.


Systems Branches
----------------
main          : Shared configuration files used across most systems
cloud         : Self-hosted, customised Linux Mint server
darwin        : macOS daily driver
devcontainer  : Lightweight configs for dev containers
edge          : Raspberry Pi edge server
wsl           : Windows Subsystem for Linux environment


Legacy Setup
----------------
Historically, all configs were kept in the same branch, with separate dirs for
different systems. This setup is preserved in the "x/system" branch. Configs for
tools I no longer use are in the "x/tools" branch.


Install
----------------
The install.sh script installs all the required dependencies and creates the
necessary symlinks to set up the system. Clone the repository and run the script
specifying preferred configuration.

Alternatively, for a more detailed control and access to other cool stripts, use
my interactive shell script with the following command:

$ wget -qO- https://karsh.page/terminal | sh

